[2
Date: 30 Aug 2001 11:22:06 EDT
From: Dr. Raja Varma <RjVarma@aol.com>

Could it be scrub typhus (mite-borne) which has been recorded from the
island; there were major outbreaks during World War II. Serological tests
should be able to confirm this.
